OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FAs Andy Burnham achieves his decades-
OL,7,Flong ambition of becoming the UK's
OL,8,Fprime minister on Monday, by his side
OL,9,Fwill be his wife of 25 years, Marie-
OL,10,FFrance van Heel.
OL,12,FBut who is the one-time game show
OL,13,Fcontestant and marketing boss who is
OL,14,Fabout to move into Downing Street?
OL,16,FMs van Heel, nicknamed Frankie, was
OL,17,Fdescribed as "the coolest girl in
OL,18,Fcollege" when she met fellow
OL,19,Fundergraduate Mr Burnham at
OL,20,FFitzwilliam College, Cambridge, in
OL,21,F1989.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
