OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FMr Burnham was in his second year
OL,7,Fstudying English when the pair bonded
OL,8,Fover a shared love of The Smiths.
OL,10,FTheir relationship took an unusual
OL,11,Fturn when she went on Cilla Black's
OL,12,FITV show Blind Date in 1992.
OL,14,FMr Burnham said he watched the
OL,15,Fprogramme from behind the sofa.
OL,17,FMs van Heel, wearing a yellow headband
OL,18,Fover her blonde bob, chose "Will from
OL,19,FSurrey", who was wearing dungarees
OL,20,Fover a red jumper.
OL,26,@zD@\OU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
