OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FLuckily for Mr Burnham, the duo did
OL,7,Fnot hit it off, with Ms van Heel
OL,8,Fthrowing a cushion at her TV date, who
OL,9,Fdescribed her as a "cold fish".
OL,11,F"Will from Surrey", otherwise known as
OL,12,FWill Harris, went on to become a
OL,13,Fmarketing director for the
OL,14,FConservative Party.
OL,16,FDutch-born Ms van Heel and Mr Burnham
OL,17,Fmarried in 2000 and had their first
OL,18,Fchild of three ` a son and two
OL,19,Fdaughters ` that year.
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@^O]sD@AOUsD@RO]
