OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FThe family, who have a bichon frise
OL,7,Fnamed Axel, are said to be tight-knit.
OL,9,FProfessionally, Ms van Heel has spent
OL,10,Fmuch of her career in marketing.
OL,12,FAfter working at BSkyB, she founded
OL,13,FMVH Marketing, and later became chief
OL,14,Fstrategy officer at London-based
OL,15,Fagency Heavenly, which has worked on
OL,16,Fcampaigns for HSBC, England Rugby and
OL,17,Fthe BBC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
