OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FShe is now chief marketing officer at
OL,7,FIduna Infrastructure, a firm which
OL,8,Fowns large parts of Manchester's
OL,9,Felectric vehicle charging network.
OL,11,FAfter questions about a possible
OL,12,Fconflict of interest, Mr Burnham, as
OL,13,FGreater Manchester mayor, distanced
OL,14,Fhimself from decisions about Iduna and
OL,15,Fdeclared his wife's job.
OL,17,FMs van Heel has largely stayed out of
OL,18,Fthe limelight since her husband first
OL,19,Fbecame an MP in 2001.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
