OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham's wife, Marie-
OL,4,CFrance van Heel?
OL,6,FShe did not join Mr Burnham on stage
OL,7,Fafter his speech accepting the Labour
OL,8,Fleadership.
OL,10,FBut they were pictured embracing in
OL,11,Fthe hall of the TUC's headquarters in
OL,12,FLondon, where their children also sat
OL,13,Fin the front row.
OL,15,FIt remains to be seen how visible she
OL,16,Fchooses to be once she takes up
OL,17,Fresidence in No 10 as the prime
OL,18,Fminister's spouse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
